	Scarlett pizzas    
	 London, Dec. 29 (PTI): She looks drop dead gorgeous thanks to her stunning looks and suave figure.      
	However, that does not stop actress Scarlett Johansson from spending her New Years eve eating pizzas.      
	The 25-year-old actress plans to eat pizzas, sip champagne and watch the cult TV series The Twilight Zone with husband Ryan Reynolds.       
	Were both working on New Years day anyway. So, we wont do much. You know, pizza would be nice, a little champagne. Maybe watch the Twilight Zone marathon. Thats always a favourite for me, Johansson said.    
	Norah Fall    
	Los Angeles (PTI): Singer Norah Jones believes that turning 30 helped her record a more personal album as she changed her creative approach to music. The Dont Know Why singer believes reaching the milestone in March forced her to reassess her life and had a change in her creative approach to making The Fall.     
	Kate time    
	 London (PTI): Actress Kate Hudson engaged in some retail therapy to recover from her break-up with baseball player Alex A-Rod Rodriguez. The 30-year-old star was seen shopping at Ralph Lauren with model Elle Macpherson before they decided to have ice creamat a nearby bakery. Kate is a serial dater, but it seems like she wants to take some time off, a source said. The actress and Rodriguez ended their relationship earlier this month.                                                                                                                                                      
